        {
            "title": "財經｜《金融時報》：怡和擬收購長和(00001)旗下百佳 或與惠康合併",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜《金融時報》：怡和擬收購長和(00001)旗下百佳 或與惠康合併\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜《金融時報》：怡和擬收購長和(00001)旗下百佳 或與惠康合併</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"英國《金融時報》\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:英國《金融時報》;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/英國《金融時報》\">英國《金融時報》</a>引述消息報道，怡和正與長和(00001)洽談收購後者的超市業務百佳超市，並將其與惠康合併。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士表示，談判已經持續一段時間，但短期內仍不會達成協議。2023年時，百佳同惠康加起來已佔香港超市市場份額近90%。惟由於近年市場競爭加劇，一名參與人士指，根據內部評估，百佳與惠康合併後的市場份額或將低於50%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報道又指，長和也在考慮讓屈臣氏集團上市，並尋求高達300億美元的估值。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">怡和表示，不對傳言或猜測發表評論。</p></div>",
