        {
            "title": "劍橋科技AH股同步創新高！H股盤中狂飆37%，A股直線升停",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周五，4月17日，劍橋科技 (HK:6166) (SS:603083)AH股同步創新高，H股盤中狂飆37%最高觸及125.9港元，A股升停報145.29元人民幣。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"582\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eebjE3WMt2lBzp8jzIKqlw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/d2c263522af8622859f29d125dcd62cd\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"579\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q0o38yao4FPnE4OPEmDCZg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/ec3eb8b9f0ea52a8842470e10e3a42e0\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息面上，光模組龍頭業績超預期引爆板塊情緒。中際旭創發佈2026年第一季度財報——營收194.96億元，同比增長192.12%；歸母淨利潤57.35億元，同比增長262.28%，均大幅超出市場預期。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-df9e28c6-5fa9-3047-93db-c9b58fcb3e85-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全球光通信器件龍頭Lumentum近期表示，數據中心需求高景氣下，現有產能已供不應求，預計兩個季度後2028年產能將全部售罄。中國銀河證券據此指出，AI驅動光模組加速反覆運算，800G/1.6T光模組迎來快速放量，高速光模組帶動測試儀器需求增長。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>財報季，美股數字睇到眼花？</span></u></strong> <strong><u><span>Warren AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>一鍵解讀數據！現在</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"772\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Wt4Lo0Tr4_EMv09bvb1GzA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc3Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/7bc1fe50cbfbb40a3c1bb504ac3fa580\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><span><br/></span></p></blockquote></div>",
